{"tid":2492194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警隊：過去一年駐守隔離營凶險萬分 正命林鄭改善職系架構","createTime":"2021-04-17T02:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T02:41:41.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0c1a4cf88e951c9d948a2bc8b3149a0a8b15f3","tid":2492194,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"警察學院早上舉行結業禮暨閱操儀式 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察學院早上舉行結業會操，由紀律人員薪俸及服務條件常務委員會主席崔康常主持。崔康常指，警隊一直對維護社會安定繁榮有重要貢獻，過去一年警隊亦大力協助防疫工作，包括駐守檢疫中心和執行隔離令，挑戰有增無減。他指，紀常會正進行紀律部隊職系架構檢討，稍後會向行政長官提出建議，相信會有利警隊長遠健康發展，令社會受惠。今日結業共有157名警員、見習督察和警署警長委任督察。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2387629&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=2f79334e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387629</a>"},{"pid":"be92fa680cafc597e47ea9c5226f49f272e634dc","tid":2492194,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"又想呃人工 呃福利"},{"pid":"8d0dc92016c608e0c5da36d5729f2059ca80c8f3","tid":2492194,"uid":133183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"建議入職五年即贈浩園長生位一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d059495480fb51b76395dfb29e04fc62f3d3ef","tid":2492194,"uid":7323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">屌你老母黑狗死全家啦<br />\n守隔離營咪又係行行企企，企到無雷公咁遠。</span>"},{"pid":"1136d69d0eab5c1eb9183839964c5c7bc0e50f20","tid":2492194,"uid":207247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"咁醫護呢？唔危險？"},{"pid":"89018c88e35db605c5961f5622b0ffe77c2c2ef9","tid":2492194,"uid":298757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"醫護都未出聲啦 屌你老母！！"},{"pid":"476de62ccbebfe79ffe7c24a08ac772c801cad8c","tid":24921